%20Microsoft%2C%20Alphabet%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Meta%2C%20Tesla%2C%20Broadcom%2C%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%2C%20and%20Walmart%20are%20worth%20around%20%2421%20trillion%20together%20%E2%80%94%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20roughly%20%2450%20trillion%20market%20cap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAverage%20Americans%20buy%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index%20ETFs%2C%20in%20part%2C%20because%20Buffett%20told%20them%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Palihapitiya%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20told%20they%20would%20pay%20very%20little%20and%20get%20diversification%20in%20the%20500%20best%20companies%20on%20earth%20to%20ride%20out%20storms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Social%20Capital%20CEO%20and%20early%20Facebook%20investor%20said%20the%20outsize%20weighting%20of%20a%20few%20stocks%20means%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhen%20you%20buy%20an%20index%20of%20500%20companies%2C%20you're%20really%20buying%2010%20companies%20with%20490%20others%20thrown%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalihapitiya%20said%20the%20lack%20of%20diversification%20means%20that%20if%20Big%20Tech%20stocks%20take%20a%20hit%2C%20investors%20could%20suffer%20huge%20losses%20as%20the%20pain%20to%20their%20portfolios%20won't%20be%20tempered%20much%20by%20other%20holdings.%20Amateur%20buyers%20face%20a%20%26quot%3Brude%20awakening%20if%20this%20isn't%20addressed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20Palihapitiya%20has%20been%20widely%20criticized%20for%20promoting%20high-risk%20special%20purpose%20acquisition%20deals%20(SPACs)%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20showing%20little%20remorse%20when%20their%20value%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fchamath-palihapitiya-spacs-companies-investing-clover-sodi-virgin-opendoor-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecratered%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%2C%20a%20value%20investor%20who%20strives%20to%20remain%20within%20his%20circle%20of%20competence%2C%20has%20largely%20eschewed%20tech%20stocks%20throughout%20his%20career%20as%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20expensive%20and%20he%20lacks%20expert%20knowledge%20of%20what%20they%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20he's%20counted%20Apple%20as%20Berkshire's%20largest%20position%20by%20far%20for%20the%20better%20part%20of%20a%20decade%2C%20despite%20paring%20that%20wager%20in%20recent%20quarters.%20The%20famed%20investor%20and%20Berkshire%20CEO%20has%20also%20hailed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-says-google-has-some-aspects-of-a-natural-monopoly-2017-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlphabet%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-facebook-meta-stock-charlie-munger-privacy-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20extraordinary%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Berkshire%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-berkshire-hathaway-economy-consumer-spending-demand-recession-homes-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextremely%20diversified%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20owning%20scores%20of%20businesses%20including%20Geico%2C%20See's%20Candies%2C%20and%20Pilot%20Travel%20Centers.%20It%20also%20holds%20billion-dollar%20stakes%20in%20listed%20companies%20such%20as%20Coca-Cola%20and%20Bank%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20has%20previously%20shrugged%20off%20shareholders'%20concerns%20about%20his%20stock%20portfolio%20being%20overly%20concentrated%20in%20Apple.%20But%20he%20might%20feel%20less%20comfortable%20now%20than%20in%20the%20past%20with%20amateur%20investors%20buying%20an%20index%20that's%20so%20dominated%20by%20a%20few%20Big%20Tech%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-spx-index-fund-chamath-tech-stocks-tracker-apple-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735640771000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6772bf049de00e389eb3c8bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-spx-index-fund-chamath-tech-stocks-tracker-apple-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stocks%20like%20Tesla%20and%20Nvidia%20now%20make%20up%20a%20huge%20chunk%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20total%20value%2C%20exposing%20investors%20to%20heavy%20losses%20if%20they%20tumble.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-spx-index-fund-chamath-tech-stocks-tracker-apple-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20bank%20disclaimer%20played%20a%20role%20in%20massive%20deposit%20losses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221914%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hand%20on%20phone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6751cb6434ef9f0108f4e520%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22957%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Jenny%20Chang-Rodriguez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202024%2C%20Jay%20Newbern%20tried%20to%20pay%20for%20his%20sushi%20dinner%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Hawaii%20when%20the%20waiter%20returned%20and%20notified%20him%20that%20his%20debit%20card%20had%20been%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20if%20they%20could%20run%20it%20again%20and%20was%20told%20they%20had%20tried%20three%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20Newbern%20wasn't%20concerned.%20After%20all%2C%20the%2034-year-old%20senior%20sales%20engineer%20had%20almost%20%24160%2C000%20in%20the%20account%20and%20assumed%20it%20was%20an%20issue%20with%20the%20card.%20So%2C%20after%20paying%20with%20another%20card%2C%20he%20tested%20it%20at%20a%20convenience%20store%2C%20only%20to%20have%20it%20declined%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20quick%20Google%20search%20found%20that%20accounts%20from%20Juno%20Finance%2C%20the%20app%20he%20used%2C%20had%20been%20frozen%20due%20to%20the%20bankruptcy%20of%20a%20partner%20fintech%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spent%20the%20next%20three%20nights%20not%20on%20the%20beach%2C%26quot%3B%20Newbern%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20spent%20them%20in%20my%20hotel%20room%2C%20suddenly%20becoming%20an%20expert%20on%20banking%2C%20regulations%2C%20financial%20technology%2C%20and%20reading%20news%20stories%20from%20financial%20publications%20I'd%20never%20heard%20of%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20hadn't%20planned%20to%20use%20the%20Juno%20account%20for%20large%20sums%2C%20but%20after%20he%20received%20a%20notice%20that%20they%20offered%20a%205%25%20APY%20in%202023%2C%20he%20transferred%20%24135%2C000%20from%20another%20account.%20He%20also%20increased%20his%20direct%20deposit%20through%20his%20company's%20payroll%20portal%20so%20that%20a%20portion%20of%20his%20paycheck%20would%20go%20there%2C%20too.%20By%20May%2C%20he%20had%20a%20balance%20of%20nearly%20%24159%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20transaction%20statements%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewbern%20was%20under%20the%20impression%20that%20his%20deposit%20was%20safe%20with%20Juno's%20so-called%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Ffdic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20FDIC-insured%3C%2Fa%3E%20partner%2C%20Evolve%20Bank%20and%20Trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20following%20weeks%2C%20he%20received%20notifications%20that%20auto%20payments%20for%20his%20phone%20bill%2C%20utilities%2C%20and%20car%20insurance%20were%20bouncing.%20When%20he%20called%20Juno%20to%20determine%20when%20this%20might%20be%20resolved%2C%20they%20told%20him%20they%20weren't%20the%20bank.%20So%2C%20he%20contacted%20Evolve%20Bank%20and%20was%20told%20they%20did%20not%20have%20his%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20puzzled.%20Despite%20using%20Juno%2C%20the%20account%20routing%20number%20Newbern%20used%20belonged%20to%20Evolve%20Bank.%20Evolve%20also%20issued%20his%20debit%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJuno%20wasn't%20the%20only%20savings%20app%20that%20seemingly%20lost%20customer%20funds.%20The%20banking-as-a-service%20provider%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffintech-startup-synapsefi-cuts-workers-downturn-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Synapse%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20linked%20fintech%20companies%20like%20Juno%20to%20banks%20through%20a%20ledger%2C%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20in%20April.%20Synapse%20had%20service%20contracts%20with%20over%2020%20partner%20financial%20institutions%20directly%20or%20indirectly%2C%20100%20fintechs%2C%20and%20approximately%2010%20million%20end%20users%20through%20its%20technology%20platform%20as%20of%20January%202024%2C%20a%20filing%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Schulzinger%20was%20using%20an%20app%20called%20Yotta%2C%20a%20savings%20account%20with%20a%20sweepstakes%20component%20that%20awarded%20users%20one%20entry%20for%20every%20%2425%20they%20deposited%2C%20with%20prizes%20ranging%20from%2010%20cents%20to%20a%20%2410%20million%20jackpot.%20He%2C%20too%2C%20assumed%20his%20deposit%20was%20safe%20because%20the%20website's%20homepage%20said%20their%20accounts%20were%20held%20by%20FDIC%20member%20Evolve.%20The%20account%20information%20posted%20to%20Yotta%2C%20where%20his%20money%20was%20transferred%2C%20also%20showed%20routing%20numbers%20belonging%20to%20Evolve.%20He%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20bank%20could%20only%20reimburse%20him%20with%20about%2023%25%20of%20his%20initial%20deposit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20statement%20from%20Evolve%2C%20before%20Synapse%20collapsed%2C%20it%20had%20migrated%20some%20customer%20funds%20out%20of%20Evolve%20bank%20accounts.%20But%20Newbern%20wasn't%20aware%20his%20money%20could%20be%20moved%20from%20the%20bank%20he%20transferred%20to.%20However%2C%20the%20bank%20argues%20that%20a%20disclaimer%20provided%20to%20end%20users%20by%20Synapse%20noted%20that%20third%20parties%20like%20Synapse%20and%20Juno%20could%20instruct%20the%20bank%20to%20take%20action%20on%20deposits.%20Attorneys%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20to%20say%20that's%20not%20an%20excuse%20to%20lose%20track%20of%20the%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ac3776b-2b30-4a72-8c3b-295007045a24%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimers%20and%20terms%20of%20services%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Eric%20Helvie%2C%20Evolve%20Bank%20and%20Trust's%20SVP%20of%20marketing%20and%20communications%2C%20said%20that%20end%20users%20signed%20an%20agreement%20with%20Synapse%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20bank%20that%20included%20the%20following%20language%20in%20bold%20caps%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYOU%20UNDERSTAND%20THAT%20BY%20OPENING%20AN%20ACCOUNT%20THROUGH%20THE%20PLATFORM%20WEBSITE%2C%20YOU%20AUTHORIZE%20BANK%20TO%20ACCEPT%20ALL%20INSTRUCTIONS%20PROVIDED%20TO%20BANK%20BY%20PLATFORM%20OR%20SYNAPSE%20ON%20YOUR%20BEHALF.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20the%20provision%20authorizes%20the%20bank%20to%20accept%20instructions%20received%20from%20Synapse%2C%20including%20the%20transfer%20of%20depositor%20funds%20out%20of%20Evovle.%20The%20spokesperson%20clarified%20that%20opening%20an%20account%20directly%20with%20Evolve%20versus%20through%20a%20fintech%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20different%20situation.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20former%2C%20depositors%20are%20direct%20customers%20and%20control%20the%20movement%20of%20their%20money%20typically%2C%20without%20a%20third%20party%2C%20unless%20authorized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20also%20said%20that%20most%20of%20the%20funds%20in%20the%20Synapse%20ecosystem%20were%20in%20a%20few%20%26quot%3BFor%20the%20Benefit%20Of%26quot%3B%20accounts%2C%20which%20included%20the%20funds%20of%20multiple%20customers.%20And%20Synapse%20was%20responsible%20for%20controlling%20and%20tracking%20the%20money%20it%20had%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJames%20Stevens%2C%20a%20corporate%20banking%20and%20fintech%20lawyer%2C%20emphasized%20that%20due%20to%20that%20disclaimer%2C%20a%20customer%20would%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20arguing%20that%20they%20didn't%20understand%20the%20involvement%20of%20multiple%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20the%20agreements%20do%20not%20make%20clear%20are%20the%20roles%20of%20the%20non-banks%20in%20the%20record-keeping%20process%20related%20to%20the%20deposit%20accounts%2C%20Stevens%20said.%20And%20herein%20lies%20the%20problem%3A%20the%20FDIC%20regulations%20require%20accurate%20record%20maintenance%20for%20deposit%20insurance%20to%20be%20provided%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228574de95-722b-4d38-b309-5d7b6ced503c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere's%20the%20money%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20answer%20is%20unsatisfactory%20as%20it%20is.%20We%20don't%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Stevens%2C%20who%20said%20that%20it%20appears%20that%20there%20were%20problems%20with%20the%20ledger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20depositors%20were%20able%20to%20retrieve%20portions%20of%20their%20funds%2C%20others%20are%20still%20waiting%20for%20an%20answer.%20Specifically%2C%20there's%20an%20ongoing%20attempt%20to%20trace%20deposits%20Evolve%20claims%20are%20not%20within%20its%20ecosystem%20through%20outreach%20to%20other%20banks%20where%20transaction%20data%20could%20be%20analyzed%20to%20determine%20where%20funds%20may%20have%20ended%20up%2C%20according%20to%20a%20November%2027%20update%20from%20Evovle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20case%20that%20whatever%20users%20saw%20on%20their%20app%20was%20told%20to%20them%20by%20the%20intermediary%20that%20was%20charged%20with%20account%20ledgering%2C%20and%20that%20money%20did%20not%20actually%20exist%20at%20that%20particular%20bank%20at%20that%20time%2C%20said%20Stevens%2C%20who%20co-authored%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.troutmanpepperfinancialservices.com%2F2024%2F10%2Fwhere-the-fbo-is-the-money-part-2-adopting-the-right-lessons-from-synapse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20an%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20noted%20there%20were%20significant%20discrepancies%20in%20Synapse's%20account%20ledgers%20that%20were%20%26quot%3Bmaterially%20inaccurate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStevens%20noted%20that%20user%20interface%20platforms%20partnering%20with%20an%20FDIC-insured%20bank%20is%20a%20common%20and%20successfully%20used%20model.%20However%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20operation%20was%20poorly%20executed.%20The%20bank%20outsourced%20the%20account%20ledger%20process%20to%20Synapse%2C%20a%20third%20party.%20And%20upon%20its%20demise%2C%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20determine%20who%20was%20owed%20what.%20In%20these%20types%20of%20setups%2C%20the%20bank%20should%20have%20overseen%20the%20efforts%20of%20their%20intermediaries%20and%20fintech%20customers%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20Newbern%20received%20an%20email%20from%20Evolve's%20founder%20and%20former%20chairman%2C%20Scot%20Lenoir%2C%20notifying%20him%20that%20until%20October%2011%2C%202023%2C%20his%20account%20showed%20a%20balance%20of%20%24153%2C679.14.%20But%20by%20October%2012%2C%20his%20balance%20was%20zero.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELenoir%20said%20the%20reason%20was%20that%20%26quot%3BJuno%2C%20through%20Synapse%2C%20migrated%20its%20program%20away%20from%20Evolve%20to%20Synapse%20Brokerage%2C%20an%20SEC-registered%20broker-dealer%2C%20member%20of%20FINRA%20and%20SIPC%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20Evolve%2C%20Newbern%20also%20obtained%20an%20October%20Synapse%20Brokerage%20statement%2C%20previously%20unavailable%20to%20him%2C%20showing%20his%20money%20was%20moved%20to%20Synapse%20Brokerage%20on%20October%2018.%20This%20transaction%20was%20not%20visible%20on%20Newbern's%20end-user%20statement%20from%20Juno.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20later%20Synapse%20Brokerage%20statement%20from%20February%20showed%20most%20of%20his%20balance%20was%20then%20transferred%20back%20to%20Evolve.%20However%2C%20Lenoir's%20response%20was%20that%20Synapse%20Brokerage%20generated%20the%20transaction%2C%20and%20they%20did%20not%20receive%20the%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESynapse's%20founder%2C%20Sankaet%20Pathak%2C%20was%20contacted%20but%20refused%20to%20comment%20without%20guarantee%20that%20this%20story%20would%20only%20place%20blame%20on%20Evolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20should%20have%20had%20a%20record-keeping%20system%20for%20the%20money%2C%20said%20Adam%20Gana%2C%20a%20securities%20attorney.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20just%20throw%20your%20hands%20up%20and%20say%2C%20'well%2C%20my%20middleman%20fintech%20company%20is%20down%20and%20therefore%20nobody%20can%20get%20their%20deposits'%2C%26quot%3B%20Gana%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20how%20this%20works.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20had%20found%20that%20Evolve%20had%20insufficient%20risk%20management%20policies.%20And%20in%20June%20it%20ordered%20the%20bank%20to%20strengthen%20those%20programs%20in%20relation%20to%20its%20fintech%20partnerships%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Ffinance%2Ffed-penalizes-evolve-bank-failing-manage-fintech-partnership-risk-2024-06-14%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewbern%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20unaware%20these%20transactions%20were%20taking%20place%20on%20his%20account%20and%20continued%20to%20view%20his%20balance%20on%20Juno%2C%20make%20deposits%2C%20and%20use%20his%20debit%20card%20from%20October%202023%20to%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20June%20email%20to%20him%2C%20Juno%20said%20they%20notified%20users%20of%20the%20migration%20in%20October%202023%20through%20a%20notice%20of%20the%20changes%20to%20its%20terms%20of%20service%20via%20email%2C%20push%20notification%2C%20and%20banners.%20The%20email%20also%20said%20that%20email%20communications%20sent%20after%20October%2017%20had%20disclosures%20menti