0came%20to%20the%20forefront.%20The%20year%20began%20with%20the%20party%20fresh%20from%20victories%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%20The%20primary%20focus%2C%20however%2C%20was%20on%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20was%20about%20expanding%20its%20political%20footprint%20wherever%20possible%20while%20relying%20on%20its%20coalition%20partners%20when%20necessary.%20In%20Haryana%2C%20the%20BJP%20went%20alone%2C%20ending%20its%20alliance%20with%20the%20JJP.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20the%20BJP%20brought%20Nitish%20Kumar%20back%20into%20the%20NDA%20fold%20and%20drew%20the%20JD(S)%20in%20Karnataka%20into%20an%20alliance%20to%20put%20up%20a%20united%20fight%20against%20Congress%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20Odisha%2C%20after%20prolonged%20negotiations%20with%20the%20BJD%2C%20the%20BJP%20decided%20to%20contest%20alone.%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Punjab%2C%20the%20BJP%20formed%20new%20alliances%20to%20challenge%20the%20bi-polar%20political%20competition%20in%20these%20states.%20In%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20became%20the%20junior%20partner%20to%20the%20TDP-Jana%20Sena%20combination%20by%20bringing%20them%20into%20the%20NDA%20to%20challenge%20both%20Congress%20and%20the%20YSR%20Congress.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20included%20minor%20partners%20with%20strong%20local%20influence%20into%20the%20NDA.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20BJP%20succeeded%20in%20ensuring%20splits%20among%20the%20two%20major%20regional%20players%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20NCP%2C%20and%20brought%20factions%20of%20both%20parties%20into%20the%20NDA.%20The%20party%20hoped%20that%20these%20efforts%20to%20expand%20its%20reach%20across%20the%20country's%20electoral%20map%20would%20yield%20political%20dividends.%20The%20slogan%20%26quot%3B400%2B%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20by-product%20of%20the%20confidence%20the%20BJP%20had%20gained%20from%20its%20coalition-building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20of%20the%202024%20elections%20indicated%20that%20while%20most%20of%20the%20coalition%20partners%20(except%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Punjab)%20managed%20to%20put%20up%20a%20creditable%20performance%2C%20the%20BJP's%20own%20performance%20left%20much%20to%20be%20desired.%20The%20BJP's%20allies%20won%2053%20seats%20in%202024%2C%20compared%20to%2050%20in%202019.%20The%20BJP's%20own%20seat%20tally%20fell%20from%20303%20in%202019%20to%20240%20in%202024%E2%80%94a%20difference%20of%2063%20seats.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20compelled%20to%20declare%20a%20victory%20for%20the%20NDA%20coalition%2C%20as%20it%20fell%20short%20of%20the%20majority%20mark%20on%20its%20own.%20With%20the%20return%20of%20a%20genuine%20coalition%20era%2C%20many%20anticipated%20visible%20changes%20in%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20new%20government.%20It%20was%20expected%20that%20notional%20representation%20for%20partners%20would%20be%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20ministry%20took%20oath%2C%20coalition%20partners%20received%20representation%20in%20the%20cabinet.%20The%20portfolio%20distribution%20mirrored%20what%20was%20seen%20in%202014%20and%202019.%20The%20BJP%20leadership%20skilfully%20managed%20to%20accommodate%20the%20coalition%20partners.%20Key%20players%E2%80%94such%20as%20the%20JDU%20and%20TDP%E2%80%94were%20more%20focused%20on%20securing%20special%20attention%20for%20their%20states%2C%20where%20they%20were%20in%20power%2C%20rather%20than%20simply%20cabinet%20berths.%20The%20agreement%20seemed%20to%20be%20that%20key%20coalition%20partners%20would%20have%20a%20say%20in%20state%20politics%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20would%20manage%20the%20national%20government.%20The%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20had%20insisted%20on%20a%20cabinet%20berth%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20was%20unwilling%20to%20accede%20to%20the%20demand%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20party%20having%20no%20representation%20in%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20test%20of%20the%20BJP's%20coalition%20skills%20was%20evident%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20and%20Jharkhand%20elections.%20The%20party%20succeeded%20in%20Maharashtra%20but%20did%20not%20reap%20electoral%20dividends%20in%20Jharkhand.%20Jharkhand%20deserves%20attention%20first.%20The%20BJP%20managed%20to%20secure%20a%20lion's%20share%20of%20seats%20within%20the%20NDA%20when%20distributing%20assembly%20tickets%20in%20the%20state.%20It%20fielded%20most%20of%20the%20candidates%20in%20the%20non-tribal%20seats%2C%20leaving%20many%20of%20the%20tribal%20seats%20to%20its%20alliance%20partners.%20However%2C%20the%20inability%20of%20the%20alliance%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20the%20non-tribal-dominated%20seats%20and%20make%20inroads%20into%20tribal%20areas%20led%20to%20the%20JMM-led%20coalition%20returning%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20Maharashtra%20was%20quite%20different.%20In%20the%20three-party%20NDA%20alliance%20(called%20the%20Mahayuti%20in%20Maharashtra)%2C%20the%20BJP%20negotiated%20for%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20seats%2C%20leaving%20the%20Shinde%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20to%20divide%20the%20remaining%20seats.%20When%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20split%20and%20the%20Shinde%20faction%20backed%20the%20BJP%20to%20form%20the%20government%2C%20the%20chief%20ministership%20was%20given%20to%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20breakaway%20Shiv%20Sena.%20Although%20the%20Mahayuti%20had%20a%20sitting%20chief%20minister%2C%20it%20did%20not%20formally%20declare%20him%20as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate.%20Both%20the%20manner%20of%20seat%20distribution%20and%20the%20silence%20on%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20were%20clearly%20part%20of%20the%20BJP's%20coalition%20management%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20results%20came%20in%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20Mahayuti%20had%20achieved%20a%20historic%20victory%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20itself%20recording%20its%20best-ever%20performance.%20Soon%20after%20the%20trends%20in%20Maharashtra%20became%20clear%2C%20by%20the%20afternoon%20of%20November%2023%2C%20the%20focus%20shifted%20to%20the%20choice%20of%20chief%20minister.%20Would%20the%20incumbent%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20be%20given%20another%20term%2C%20or%20would%20the%20BJP%20claim%20the%20chief%20ministership%2C%20given%20its%20spectacular%20performance%3F%20This%20became%20the%20central%20point%20of%20debate.%20The%20suspense%20continued%20for%20more%20than%2010%20days%20after%20the%20results%20were%20declared.%20Over%20these%20ten%20days%2C%20the%20partners%20and%20their%20leaders%20were%20gradually%20brought%20around.%20Ajit%20Pawar%20of%20the%20NCP%20was%20the%20easiest%20to%20convince%2C%20while%20Eknath%20Shinde%20held%20out%20for%20longer%20but%20ultimately%20gave%20in.%20This%20showcased%20the%20negotiation%20skills%20of%20the%20BJP%20leadership.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20party%20also%20convinced%20Shinde%20to%20accept%20the%20position%20of%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20which%20he%20finally%20agreed%20to.%20The%20final%20two%20rounds%20of%20negotiations%20focused%20on%20the%20distribution%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20council%20of%20ministers%20and%20the%20allocation%20of%20portfolios.%20The%20more%20difficult%20negotiation%20seemed%20to%20be%20on%20portfolios%2C%20particularly%20the%20one%20for%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister.%20Shinde%20was%20believed%20to%20be%20insisting%20on%20the%20home%20portfolio%20but%20ultimately%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20urban%20development%20and%20a%20few%20other%20ministries.%20A%20review%20of%20the%20portfolios%20shows%20that%20the%20BJP%20ministers%20secured%20a%20better%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20demonstrated%20the%20BJP's%20capacity%20to%20drive%20negotiations%20with%20its%20coalition%20partners%20in%20its%20favour.%20With%20crucial%20state%20elections%20in%202025%2C%20it%20will%20be%20closely%20watched%20whether%20this%20trend%20continues%20or%20if%20there%20is%20a%20reversal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dr.%20Sandeep%20Shastri%20is%20the%20National%20Coordinator%20of%20the%20Lokniti%20Network)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735638360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fqe3mh1qg_pm-modi-road-show-ghaziabad_625x300_06_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-bjp-managed-allies-in-2024-7370008%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20year%20demonstrated%20the%20BJP's%20capacity%20to%20drive%20negotiations%20with%20its%20coalition%20partners%20in%20its%20favour.%20With%20crucial%20state%20elections%20in%202025%2C%20it%20will%20be%20closely%20watched%20whether%20this%20trend%20continues%20or%20if%20there%20will%20be%20a%20reversal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Punjabi%20Singer%20Ranjit%20Bawa%20receives%20extortion%20call%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735637562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116826957%2Cimgsize-75170.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fpunjabi%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fpunjabi-singer-ranjit-bawa-receives-extortion-call-security-enhanced-amid-rising-threats%2Farticleshow%2F116826979.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116826979.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPunjabi%20singer%20Ranjit%20Bawa%20has%20reportedly%20received%20an%20extortion%20call%20from%20an%20unidentified%20person.%20His%20manager%2C%20Malkit%20Singh%2C%20filed%20a%20complaint%2C%20revealing%20threats%20demanding%20money.%20The%20police%20have%20taken%20swift%20action%20by%20registering%20the%20case%20and%20increasing%20Bawa%E2%80