C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAgora%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20financial%20software%20firm%20that%20helps%20real-estate%20investors%20process%20payments%2C%20keep%20track%20of%20tax%20records%2C%20raise%20money%2C%20and%20generally%20organize%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20it's%20hot%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20firm%2C%20which%20raised%20a%20%2434%20million%20Series%20B%20round%20in%20May%2C%20said%20it%20helps%20landlords%20and%20developers%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewith%20much-needed%20modernization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReal%20estate%20is%20the%20largest%20asset%20class%20in%20the%20world.%20However%2C%20the%20market%20still%20relies%20on%20legacy%20software%20providers%2C%20inefficient%20workflows%2C%20outdated%2C%20fragmented%20systems%2C%20and%20manual%2C%20tedious%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Asaf%20Raz%2C%20Agora's%20head%20of%20marketing%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20expect%20a%20digital-first%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20tech-savvy%20and%20need%20access%20to%20information%20quickly.%20Firms%20can't%20work%20without%20it%2C%20and%20clients%20need%20a%20platform%20like%20Agora%20more%20than%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20Raz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20challenge%20it%20faces%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EReal-estate%20investors%20are%20still%20grappling%20with%20relatively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-mortgage-rates-come-down-real-estate-investing-strategies-biggerpockets-2024-2%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThat%2527s%2520fairly%2520consistent%2520with%2520what%2Cto%2520Business%2520Insider%2527s%2520Molly%2520Grace.%26amp%3Btext%3DHigh%2520rates%2520are%2520bad%2520news%2Cgood%2520for%2520strategies%2520like%2520flipping.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20interest%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20harder%20to%20borrow%20money%20and%20scale%20up%2C%20and%20the%20relatively%20high%20price%20of%20materials%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20tougher%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fw