nessinsider.com%2Fhomes-real-estate-how-to-fix-housing-crisis-factors-construction-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehousing%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20particularly%20acute%20in%20California%2C%20which%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-apartment-rent-housing-shortage-crisis-solution-laws-prices-decline-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassed%20a%20series%20of%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20encourage%20more%20building.%20While%20others%20look%20to%20transform%20construction%20to%20make%20cheaper%20housing%2C%20BuildCasa%20uses%20technology%20instead%20to%20find%20more%20buildable%20lots%20in%20desirable%20locations%20like%20San%20Francisco%20and%20San%20Jose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20massive%20home-building%20companies%20focus%20on%20large%2C%20master-planned%20communities%2C%20often%20far%20from%20city%20centers.%20BuildCasa's%20vision%2C%20said%20its%20founders%20Ben%20Bear%2C%20CEO%2C%20and%20Paul%20Stiedl%2C%20CPO%2C%20is%20to%20become%20a%20large%20homebuilder%20focused%20instead%20on%20finding%20land%20in%20already%20desirable%20cities%20and%20suburbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20works%20with%20homeowners%20to%20subdivide%20their%20land%2C%20creating%20a%20new%2C%20buildable%20lot.%20Those%20lots%20can%20then%20be%20sold%20to%20a%20local%20real-estate%20developer%20to%20build%20on%2C%20or%20BuildCasa%20can%20work%20in%20partnership%20with%20a%20local%20builder%20to%20erect%20and%20then%20sell%20a%20completed%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20challenge%20it%20faces%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENew%20laws%20have%20simplified%20the%20process%20of%20subdividing%20lots%2C%20but%20building%20in%20infill%20areas%20still%20requires%20technical%20expertise%20and%20good%20relationships%20with%20local%20officials.%20Building%20on%20these%20smaller%20lots%20may%20be%20becoming%20%3Cem%3Eeasier%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20but%20it%20still%20isn't%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EConservation%20Labs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22431%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20headshot%20of%20a%20man%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66509cd7239fda2da6cb5c93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22521%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConservation%20Labs%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Mark%20Kovscek.%3Cp%3EConservation%20Labs%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPittsburgh%2C%20Pennsylvania%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYear%20founded%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202018%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotal%20funding%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2414.68%20million%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20does%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EConservation%20Labs%20developed%20a%20smart%20water%20sensor%20that%20can%20identify%20leaks%20and%20wasteful%20water%20use.%20The%20H2know%20sensor%20uses%20machine%20learning%20to%20decode%20sounds%20in%20water%20pipes%20and%20translate%20them%20into%20insights%20for%20commercial%20property%20owners%2C%20including%20restaurants%20and%20hotels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20it's%20hot%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20startup%20is%20at%20the%20intersection%20of%20two%20buzzy%20topics%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAI%20and%20sustainability.%20H2know%20trains%20on%20thousands%20of%20hours%20of%20water%20pipe%20acoustics%20so%20that%2C%20over%20time%2C%20it%20becomes%20more%20accurate%20in%20detecting%20leaks%20and%20inefficient%20water%20use%20in%20buildings.%20Customers%20use%20that%20information%20to%20fix%20problems%20and%20conserve%20water%2C%20saving%20them%20money%20on%20utility%20bills%20while%20lowering%20their%20overall%20carbon%20footprint.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.energy.gov%2Fenergysaver%2Fwater-heating%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E20%25%20of%20home%20energy%20use%3C%2Fa%3E%20goes%20to%20heating%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20very%20strong%20relationship%20between%20net-zero%20carbon%20emissions%20and%20water%20consumption%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mark%20Kovscek%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Conservation%20Labs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20H2know%20has%20detected%20leaky%20toilets%20in%20nearly%20every%20building%20in%20which%20it's%20installed.%20Some%20large%20properties%20are%20wasting%201%20million%20gallons%20of%20water%20a%20year%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20challenge%20it%20faces%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20H2know%20starts%20at%20%24129%2C%20and%20it%20could%20be%20hard%20to%20convince%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-big-trouble-crash-bank-crisis-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecash-strapped%20commercial%20real%20estate%20owners%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20spend%20money%20to%20install%20sensors%20when%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foffice-market-collapse-outlook-commercial-real-estate-foreclosures-default-debt-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffice%20market%20is%20struggling%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKovscek%20said%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20scale%20up%20to%20100%2C000%20sensors%20installed%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20or%20five%20times%20what%20Conservation%20Labs%20is%20currently%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20track%20to%20sell%20this%20year.%20To%20support%20that%20growth%2C%20the%20company%20needs%20to%20hire%20some%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%20and%20brightest%26quot%3B%20data%20scientists%20and%20engineers%20to%20further%20develop%20the%20machine-learning%20platform%20that%20underpins%20H2know%2C%20Kovscek%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EConstrafor%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221944%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20in%20Times%20Square.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66509d5520abc1efe8fd501c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221296%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConstrafor%20cofounders%20CTO%20Douglas%20Reed%2C%20left%2C%20and%20CEO%20Anwar%20Ghauche.%3Cp%3EConstrafor%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20New%20York%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYear%20founded%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E2019%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotal%20funding%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAlmost%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%24380%20million%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20does%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELarge%20general%20contractors%20use%20Constrafor's%20software%20to%20onboard%20and%20pay%20their%20subcontractors%20on%20time%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20before%20the%20contractors%20themselves%20get%20paid%20by%20the%20clients.%20Contractors%20can%20also%20use%20the%20software%20to%20help%20purchase%20the%20supplies%20and%20services%20needed%20to%20complete%20a%20construction%20project%20on%20time%20and%20within%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20it's%20hot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20There's%20the%20money%20raised.%20In%20November%2C%20%3Cspan%3EConstrafor%20announced%20that%20it%20raised%20%2414%20million%20in%20Series%20A%20funding%20as%20well%20as%20a%20%24250%20million%20credit%20facility.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issues%20the%20firm%20is%20trying%20to%20address%20are%20also%20key.%20Construction%20is%20booming%20across%20the%20US%2C%20thanks%20in%20part%20to%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-in-bidens-infrastructure-bill-package-american-jobs-plan-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoe%20Biden's%20%241.2%20trillion%20infrastructure%20bill%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20rise%20of%20AI%20is%20also%20leading%20to%20a%20corresponding%20increase%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-google-microsoft-ai-future-data-centers-monopoly-tech-industry-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actual%20process%20of%20construction%2C%20however%2C%20can%20often%20be%20long%20and%20complicated.%20That's%20why%20Constrafor's%20role%20as%20a%20one-stop%20shop%20appeals%20to%20large%20general%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20far%2C%20everyone%20has%20been%20focused%20on%20just%20building%20a%20very%2C%20very%20small%20point%20solution%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Anwar%20Ghauche%2C%20Constrafor's%20founder.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20combining%20multiple%20different%20workflows%2C%20multiple%20different%20departments%2C%20all%20on%20the%20same%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20main%20challenges%20it%20faces%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENext%20up%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EConstrafor%20must%20try%20to%20convince%20subcontractors%20to%20subscribe%20and%20pay%20for%20its%20software%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGauch%20added%20that%20Constrafor's%20contractor%20clients%20can%20face%20cash-flow%20crunches.%20Those%20can%20lead%20to%20delays%20on%20important%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Hurricanes%20Helene%20and%20Milton%20severely%20damaged%20parts%20of%20Florida%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20Southeast%2C%20Constrafor%20launched%20a%20disaster%20relief%20effort%20that%20would%20allow%20local%20contractors%20who%20are%20part%20of%20rebuilding%20efforts%20%26quot%3Bto%20overcome%20delays%2C%20purchase%20materials%2C%20and%20ensure%20timely%20payment%20for%20their%20teams.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEase%20Capital%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221416%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20headshots%20of%20men%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66509d9f239fda2da6cb5d64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22970%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEase%20Capital's%20Ryan%20Simonetti%2C%20Guillermo%20Sanchez%2C%20and%20Charlie%20Oshman.%3Cp%3EEase%20Capital%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENew%20York%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYear%20founded%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202022%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotal%20funding%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%2413.95%20million%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20does%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ease%20Capital%20helps%20private%20equity%20firms%20and%20large%20investors%20lend%20to%20smaller%20apartment%20landlords.%20It%20uses%20data%20and%20technology%20that%20allow%20the%20biggest%20players%20to%20lend%20%245%20million%20to%20%2450%20million%20in%20deals%20that%20would%20typically%20be%20too%20small%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20it's%20hot%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESophisticated%20private%20lenders%20usually%20focus%20on%20the%20largest%20apartment%20complexes%2C%20meaning%20that%20most%20apartment-building%20owners%20have%20to%20turn%20to%20banks%20and%20agencies%20to%20borrow%20money%20to%20purchase%20or%20refinance%20properties.%20However%2C%20current%20high%20rates%20have%20dramatically%20slowed%20bank%20and%20agency%20lending%20and%20the%20large%20private%20lenders%20usually%20won't%20lend%20for%20small%E2%80%94and%20medium-sized%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEase%20uses%20data%20and%20technology%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20and%20more%20efficient%20for%20these%20large%20lenders%20to%20lend%20on%20smaller%20deals%20when%20the%20need%20is%20the%20highest.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20a%20%24450%20million%20partnership%20with%20major%20real%20estate%20owner%20and%20asset%20manager%20Taconic%20Capital%20Partners%2C%20and%20has%20already%20announced%20multiple%20successfully%20originated%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Charlie%20Oshamn%20told%20Business%20Insider%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20the%20company%20is%20often%20seeing%20up%20to%20%241%20billion%20in%20loan%20requests%20a%20month.%20Unlike%20other%20firms%2C%20which%20provide%20an%20estimated%20rate%20upfront%20that%20could%20potentially%20change%20over%20months%20of%20negotiation%2C%20Ease%20Capital%20sticks%20to%20its%20initial%20offering%2C%20eliminating%20the%20guessing%20game%20for%20potential%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20challenge%20it%20faces%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThough%20the%20founding%20team%20has%20successfully%20launched%20other%20major%20proptech%20businesses%2C%20like%20flexible%20office%20and%20event%20space%20provider%20Convene%20and%20real-estate%20data%20firm%20Reonomy%2C%20it%20still%20needs%20to%20prove%20itself%20as%20a%20lender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHabi%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20people%20posing%20in%20an%20office%20full%20of%20people%20working.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66509dfe20abc1efe8fd5079%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrynne%20McNulty%20Rojas%2C%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Habi%2C%20left%2C%20and%20Sebastian%20Noguera%20Escallon%2C%20president%20and%20cofounder.%3Cp%3EHabi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Colombia%20and%20Mexico%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYear%20founded%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202019%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotal%20funding%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%24564%20million%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20does%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Habi%20has%20built%20Latin%20America's%20largest%20proprietary%20database%20and%20utilizes%20AI-based%20pricing%20algorithms%20to%20facilitate%20transactions%20and%20financing%20for%20homebuyers%20and%20sellers.%20Habi%20also%20buys%20and%20sells%20homes%2C%20offers%20mortgages%2C%20and%20posts%20and%20publicizes%20listings%20of%20properties%20for%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20it's%20hot%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20company%20operates%20in%20Colombia%20and%20Mexico%20without%20centralized%20MLS.%20MLS%2C%20or%20multiple%20listing%20services%2C%20are%20databases%20designed%20to%20help%20real%20estate%20brokers%20identify%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eavailable%20homes%20for%20sale.%20These%20systems%20are%20abundant%20in%20the%20US%2C%20whereas%20they%20are%20scarce%20in%20Latin%20America.%20Without%20an%20MLS%2C%20it%20means%20homebuyers%20and%20sellers%20in%20Colombia%20and%20Mexico%20have%20difficulty%20knowing%20which%20properties%20are%20available%20for%20sale%2C%20their%20prices%2C%20and%20their%20listing%20and%20pricing%20history.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20gathering%20and%20sharing%20information%20on%20more%20than%2020%20million%20homes%2C%20Habi%20has%20addressed%20a%20critical%20need%20in%20these%20countries'%20real%20estate%20sector%2C%20establishing%20itself%20as%20an%20authority%20on%20housing%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20become%20a%20household%20name%20for%20low%20and%20middle-income%20sellers%20and%20consumers%20and%20brokers%20in%20Mexico%20and%20Colombia%2C%26quot%3B%20Brynne%20McNulty%20Rojas%2C%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Habi%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20challenge%20it%20faces%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20combination%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20shifting%20economic%20and%20political%20conditions%2C%20has%20stalled%20the%20growth%20of%20Latin%20America's%20real-estate%20market.%20To%20achieve%20the%20same%20level%20of%20ubiquity%20as%20Zillow%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Habi%20must%20get%20real-estate%20brokers%20and%20sellers%20to%20list%20their%20properties%20on%20its%20platform%20and%20entice%20buyers%20to%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHoneyHomes%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Professional%20headshot%20of%20Vishwas%20Prabhakara%20in%20a%20Honey%20Homes%20polo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d0ed3c1d8d2deb96b78cda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVishwas%20Prabhakara%2C%20Founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Honey%20Homes%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Honey%20Homes%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Lafayette%2C%20California%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYear%20founded%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202021%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotal%20funding%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2421.35%20million%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20does%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Founder%20Vishwas%20Prabhakara%20envisions%20Honey%20Homes%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bprimary%20care%20physician%20for%20your%20home.%26quot%3B%20For%20a%20monthly%20fee%2C%20a%20dedicated%20handyman%20will%20come%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20month%20to%20knock%20off%20%26quot%3Blightweight%26quot%3B%20home%20improvement%20projects%20like%20fixing%20a%20leaky%20faucet%2C%20installing%20a%20new%20ceiling%20fan%2C%20or%20repainting%20a%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20it's%20hot%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20a%20cooling%20housing%20market%2C%20Prabhakara%20believes%20many%20homeowners%20are%20staying%20in%20their%20homes%20longer%20and%20interested%20in%20investing%20resources%20in%20%E2%80%94%20and%20enjoying%20%E2%80%94%20the%20property%20they%20currently%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20main%20challenge%20it%20faces%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Homeowners%20who%20already%20hire%20their%20preferred%20handymen%20may%20not%20be%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20service%20that%20sends%20new%20people%2C%20and%20bigger%20projects%20might%20require%20more%20specialized%20repair%20professionals.%20%3Cspan%3EThen%20there's%20the%20cost%20and%20current%20smaller%20scale%20of%20the%20company%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESubscriptions%20start%20from%20%24295%20a%20month%2C%20or%20%243%2C940%20a%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company%20website.%20The%20service%20is%20only%20available%20in%20parts%20of%20San%20Francisco%20and%20the%20Bay%20Area%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Orange%20County%2C%20and%20Dallas%2C%20according%20to%20the%20site.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EImpulse%20Labs%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20headshot%20of%20a%20man.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66509e6ba961b37edf39a235%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221786%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EImpulse%20Labs%20CEO%20and%20founder%20Sam%20D'Amico.%3Cp%3EImpulse%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESan%20Francisco%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYear%20founded%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202021%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETotal%20funding%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2425%20million%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20does%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EImpulse%20Labs%20made%20a%20battery-powered%20induction%20cooktop%20that%2C%20unlike%20most%20of%20its%20competitors%2C%20which%20may%20require%20an%20electrical%20upgrade%2C%20can%20plug%20into%20a%20standard%20120-volt%20outlet.%20The%20cooktop%20can%20boil%20water%20at%20lightning%20speeds%2C%20and%20sensors%20hold%20heat%20levels%20steady%20even%20at%20high%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20it's%20hot%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Impulse%20Labs%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efounder%20Sam%20D'Amico%20said%20the%20cooktop%20offers%20a%20better%20cooking%20experience%20than%20gas%20burners%20while%20promoting%20more%20climate-friendly%20homes.%20Cooking%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-stove-asthma-childhood-secondhand-smoke-lung-health-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egas%20emits%20pollutants%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20methane%2C%20benzene%2C%20and%20carbon%20monoxide%2C%20which%20harm%20our%20health%20and%20the%20planet.%20But%20it%20can%20cost%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20to%20rewire%20a%20home%20for%20an%20electric%20induction%20stove.%20Impulse%20Labs'%20induction%20cooktop%20avoids%20those%20pollutants%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20home%20retrofits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20battery%20in%20Impulse%20Labs'%20stove%20also%20stores%20enough%20power%20to%20make%20three%20meals%20if%20the%20power%20goes%20out%2C%20D'Amico%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20cheapest%20ways%20to%20deploy%20battery%20storage%20is%20in%20the%20appliances%20we%20have%20to%20buy%20anyways%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20main%20challenge%20it%20faces%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20cooktop%20costs%20%245%2C999.%20The%20price%20is%20high%2C%20D'Amico%20said%2C%20but%20similar%20to%20other%20premium%20appliances.%20The%20price%20is%20lower%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D