20refocus%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20been%20on%20ideas%2C%20research%2C%20and%20longer%20timelines.%20Instead%20of%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bcatch%20every%20wiggle%26quot%3B%20or%20make%20money%20on%20every%20market%20twitch%2C%20portfolio%20managers%20are%20being%20pushed%20to%20find%20multimonth%20or%20even%20multiquarter%20investment%20ideas%2C%20he%20said.%20The%20result%20has%20been%20lower%20position%20turnover%20and%20less%20trading%20in%20PMs'%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnovember-hedge-fund-returns-balyasny-citadel-millennium-schonfeld-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperformance%20rebounded%20in%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20After%20a%20big%20November%20that%20had%20the%20manager%20up%2011.6%25%20through%20the%20first%2011%20months%2C%20the%20manager%20is%20set%20to%20land%20squarely%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20its%20peers%20for%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20firm's%20hiring%20%E2%80%94%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-goodwin-equities-fund-launch-longaeva-balyasny-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eequities%20unit%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well%20as%20other%20strategies%20%E2%80%94%20got%20most%20of%20the%20headlines%20for%20the%20manager%20this%20year%2C%20Balyasny%20said%20it%20was%20the%20improvement%20of%20existing%20stock-picking%20teams%20that%20drove%20the%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2292a6206e-194d-435d-b296-42d1ebcf4251%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDNA%20change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBalyasny's%20equities%20struggles%20coincided%20with%20multistrategy%20firms'%20growth%20and%20hedge%20funds'%20increased%20use%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-funds-spend-even-more-alternative-data-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealternative%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20credit-card%20transactions%20and%20email%20receipts%2C%20which%20can%20provide%20a%20sneak%20peek%20of%20a%20company's%20performance%20before%20it%20reports%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20data%2C%20which%20provided%20an%20invaluable%20edge%20a%20decade%20ago%20but%20is%20now%20table%20stakes%20at%20firms%20like%20Balyasny%2C%20pushed%20investors%20to%20focus%20%26quot%3Bexcessively%20on%20triangulating%20and%20calling%20quarters%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steve%20Schurr%2C%20a%20senior%20portfolio%20manager%20who%20was%20promoted%20to%20the%20equities%20leadership%20team%20in%20mid-2023%2C%20when%20the%20%26quot%3Bcourse%20correction%26quot%3B%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20become%20a%20strategy%20of%20diminished%20expected%20returns%26quot%3B%20as%20more%20firms%20use%20this%20type%20of%20data%2C%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchurr%2C%20who%20started%20his%20career%20in%20investing%20working%20for%20the%20legendary%20short-seller%20Jim%20Chanos%2C%20performed%20well%20during%20the%20equities%20division's%20run%20of%20underperformance.%20Balyasny%20identified%20his%20focus%20on%20primary%20research%20as%20a%20winner%20and%20pushed%20him%20to%20spread%20it%20across%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20change%20the%20DNA%20of%20how%20we%20conducted%20research%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Schurr%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20built%20out%20an%20internal%20research%20database%20called%20Telescope%2C%20which%20has%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhedge-fund-balyasny-analyst-research-generative-ai-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20overlay%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20summarize%20things%20like%20podcasts%2C%20expert%20network%20calls%2C%20and%20sell-side%20research.%20A%20new%2015-person%20internal%20research%20team%20with%20data%20scientists%20and%20former%20journalists%20has%20done%20120%20projects%20for%20PMs%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchurr%20said%20he%20believed%20that%20%26quot%3Bdurable%20edge%26quot%3B%20for%20all%20multistrategy%20firms%20investing%20in%20equities%20would%20come%20through%20primary%20research%2C%20not%20alternative%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20are%20back%20to%20the%20anarchy%20of%20having%20to%20be%20good%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20multistrategy%20sector%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3B80%25%20of%20a%20portfolio%20manager's%20opportunity%20is%20going%20to%20be%20from%20equity%20selection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ed24a70b-31f4-4797-b81f-07629c2d7aa7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlayer-coaches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20industry%20has%20matured%2C%20the%20titans%20of%20the%20field%20have%20gone%20from%20brash%20traders%20to%20business-building%20executives.%20The%20leaders%20at%20Citadel%2C%20Millennium%2C%20Jain%20Global%2C%20Brevan%20Howard%2C%20and%20more%20do%20not%20run%20a%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-cohen-at-65-how-billionaire-point72-founder-has-evolved-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESteve%20Cohen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20billionaire%20founder%20of%20Point72%20and%20owner%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Mets%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-cohens-decision-to-stop-trading-is-a-big-deal-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estopped%20trading%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20summer%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20official%20end%20of%20an%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Balyasny%20has%20begun%20trading%20a%20book%20again%20for%20his%20firm%20after%20giving%20it%20up%20for%20a%20time.%20Other%20leaders%20on%20the%20equities%20team%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Schurr%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-goodwin-equities-fund-launch-longaeva-balyasny-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeter%20Goodwin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who's%20launching%20an%20internal%20stock-picking%20unit%20called%20Longaeva%20Partners%20and%20plans%20to%20hire%20PMs%20to%20work%20underneath%20him%20%E2%80%94%20are%20also%20managing%20portfolios%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalyasny%2C%20who%20has%20tapped%20people%20to%20run%20his%20quant%2C%20commodities%2C%20and%20macro%20units%2C%20isn't%20planning%20to%20hire%20someone%20to%20oversee%20equities.%20Jeff%20Runnfeldt%2C%20now%20the%20chief%20investment%20officer%20of%20Fortress'%20multimanager%20platform%2C%20oversaw%20the%20equities%20unit%2C%20but%20Balyasny%20stepped%20into%20the%20role%20on%20an%20interim%20basis%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaylasny-four-equities-pms-exit-after-top-execs-departure-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERunnfeldt%20and%20the%20firm%20parted%20ways%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20interim%20tag%20has%20been%20removed.%20Balyasny%20said%20he%20believes%20that%20trading%20alongside%20his%20employees%20helps%20him%20connect%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbalyasny-building-investment-talent-pipeline-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20recruits%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20he's%20in%20the%20trenches%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBalyasny%20has%20had%20its%20ups%20and%20downs%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%20in%202018%20when%20the%20manager%20laid%20off%2020%25%20of%20its%20staff%20and%20saw%20investors%20redeem%20%244%20billion.%20The%20circumstances%20this%20time%20around%20are%20much%20different%2C%20he%20said%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20diversification%20of%20the%20firm's%20assets%20and%20LP%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%2090%25%20of%20the%20risk%20was%20in%20equities%3B%20now%20it's%2040%25%20to%2050%25.%20The%20firm's%20investors%20were%20only%2020%25%20institutional%20in%202018%3B%20now%20that%20figure%20is%2070%25%2C%20giving%20the%20firm%20long-term%20capital%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20a%20bristecone%20pine%20tree.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e4b344d17aa3c7b2b