movies%2C%20music%2C%20etc.)%2C%20I'll%20open%20up%20PI.FYI%20to%20see%20what%20people%20are%20sharing.%20The%20app%20lets%20you%20add%20a%20link%20to%20a%20post%2C%20which%20helps%20when%20going%20down%20rabbit%20holes.%20Posting%20there%20sometimes%20feels%20like%20writing%20into%20the%20void%20on%20Tumblr%20or%20Twitter%20in%202012%20(in%20a%20good%20way).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274f52bad-85cc-465e-97b1-b097e8553962%5C%22%3E2.%20Airbuds%20lets%20you%20see%20what%20friends%20are%20listening%20to%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20Airbuds%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6772d0646e18b095615a7f2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%2FBusiness%20Insider%3B%20Airbuds%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20it%20is%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt's%20a%20feed%20of%20music.%20It's%20that%20simple.%20Airbuds%20pulls%20information%20from%20several%20music%20streaming%20platforms%20(including%20Spotify%2C%20Apple%20Music%2C%20and%20Soundcloud).%20The%20team%20behind%20Airbuds%20also%20built%20Cappuccino%2C%20a%20social-audio%20app%20that%20launched%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20Clubhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20it%20launched%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E2023%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20I%20haven't%20deleted%20it%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20switched%20from%20Spotify%20to%20Apple%20Music%20several%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20the%20one%20feature%20I%20missed%20was%20the%20ability%20to%20see%20what%20my%20friends%20were%20listening%20to.%20Airbuds%20lets%20me%20do%20just%20that%20and%20also%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20save%20music%20to%20my%20own%20library.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2284753a1e-c115-4379-899c-3576104e7c79%5C%22%3E3.%20IRL%20social%20app%20222%20coordinates%20experiences%20with%20strangers%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22222%20scre