s%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-social-media-apps-worth-downloading-irl-music-recommendations-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735635901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676b2c767236dcf54aa24c88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-social-media-apps-worth-downloading-irl-music-recommendations-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20testing%20out%20many%20new%20social-media%20apps%2C%20here%20are%20three%20worth%20trying%20out%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20alternatives%20to%20Instagram%2C%20X%2C%20or%20TikTok.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbradley%40insider.com%20(Sydney%20Bradley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-social-media-apps-worth-downloading-irl-music-recommendations-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20a%20psychologist%2C%20here's%20how%20I'm%20going%20to%20make%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20keep%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20my%20New%20Year's%20resolution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20laughing%20and%20grimacing%20lying%20on%20floor%20of%20a%20gym%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6765b15b1cee543535a88e1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20man%2C%20not%20the%20author%2C%20pushes%20his%20limits%20while%20at%20the%20gym.%3Cp%3EThomas%20Barwick%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20a%20health%20psychologist%20and%20I'm%20setting%20a%20SMART%20resolution%20for%202025.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESMART%20goals%20are%20specific%2C%20measurable%2C%20achievable%2C%20relevant%2C%20and%20time-bound%20for%20success.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20think%20consistency%20and%20self-compassion%20are%20key%20to%20turning%20resolutions%20into%20lasting%20habits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20year%202025%20is%20nearly%20here%20and%20that%20means%20it's%20time%20for%20me%20to%20set%20my%20New%20Year's%20resolution.%20I'm%20not%20alone%2C%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipsos.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fct%2Fnews%2Fdocuments%2F2024-12%2Fipsos-predictions-2025-survey-report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%20%3C%2Fa%3Efound%20that%20up%20to%2075%25%20of%20Americans%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-get-rid-of-before-2025-from-professional-organizers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaking%20resolutions%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%202025.%20But%2C%20despite%20our%20best%20intentions%2C%20many%20of%20us%20will%20fail%20to%20stick%20to%20them.%20Psychologists%20refer%20to%20this%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC6125069%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintention-action%20gap%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20health%20psychologist%20specializing%20in%20behavior%20change%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20try%20to%20practice%20what%20I%20preach%20this%20year.%20My%20own%20resolution%3F%20To%20go%20to%20the%20gym%20for%2030%20minutes%2C%20five%20times%20per%20week%20for%20six%20months.%20Here's%20how%20I%20plan%20to%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220aa65cfc-6f2e-4cda-9dc0-976570307d9f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20SMART%20resolution%20will%20set%20me%20up%20for%20success%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrigger-workout-add-to-fitness-routine-get-fit-without-gym-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoing%20to%20the%20gym%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%2030%20minutes%2C%20five%20times%20per%20week%20for%20six%20months%20is%20a%20pretty%20specific%20goal.%20Well%2C%20that's%20my%20first%20tip%20in%20setting%20SMART%20resolutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ES%20is%20for%20a%20specific%20goal.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Setting%20one%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Especific%20resolution%20rather%20than%20many%20is%20more%20achievable%20for%20many%20people.%20So%20as%20much%20as%20I%20would%20like%20to%20eat%20more%20fruit%20and%20veggies%2C%20cut%20down%20on%20my%20excessive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhow-much-caffeine-is-too-much%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoffee%20intake%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meditate%20more%2C%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20the%20kids%20etc%20(you%20get%20the%20picture)%2C%20trying%20to%20take%20on%20too%20many%20resolutions%20will%20likely%20set%20me%20up%20for%20failure.%20I'll%20stick%20to%20one%20and%20then%20maybe%20add%20another%20once%20this%20becomes%20a%20habit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EM%20is%20for%20measurable.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20me%2C%20I%20plan%20to%20keep%20a%20record%20of%20my%20workouts%2C%20and%20track%20my%20progress%20on%20the%20treadmill%20or%20the%20weights%20by%20using%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fbest-free-workout-apps%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmartphone%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20I%20can%20schedule%20and%20register%20my%20workouts.%20I%20also%20plan%20to%20use%20my%20smartphone%20for%20'digital%20nudges'%20reminders%20or%20prompts%20that%20keep%20will%20keep%20me%20motivated%20and%20on%20track.%20For%20example%2C%20I'll%20be%20scheduling%20recurring%20calendar%20appointments%20for%20my%20gym%20sessions%2C%20with%20alarms%20to%20remind%20me%20when%20it's%20time%20to%20close%20the%20laptop%20and%20get%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20is%20for%20achievable%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20As%20much%20as%20I%20would%20like%20to%20think%20I%20could%20spend%20an%20hour%20plus%20in%20the%20gym%20every%20weekday%20like%20I%20did%20when%20I%20was%20(much)%20younger%2C%20these%20days%2C%20with%20two%20young%20kids%20and%20a%20busy%20work%20life%2C%20I%20know%20it's%20not%20realistic.%20Start%20small%2C%20you%20can%20always%20extend%20your%20resolution%20later%20in%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ER%20is%20for%20relevant.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20might%20seem%20obvious%2C%20but%20many%20of%20us%20feel%20pressured%20into%20setting%20resolutions%2C%20some%20of%20which%20may%20not%20really%20be%20what%20we%20deep%20down%20want%20to%20change.%20Many%20New%20Year's%20resolutions%20are%20about%20improving%20fitness%2C%20but%20you%20might%20want%20to%20do%20something%20completely%20different%2C%20like%20taking%20up%20pottery%20or%20seeing%20your%20relatives%20more%20regularly.%20Find%20what%20matters%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20positive%20peer%20pressure%20can%20be%20a%20good%20thing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopen.ncl.ac.uk%2Ftheories%2F18%2Ftheory-of-planned-behaviour%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%20%3C%2Fa%3Eshows%20that%20we%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20adopt%20new%20behaviors%20when%20those%20that%20matter%20to%20us%20(close%20friends%20and%20family)%20approve%20of%20what%20we%20are%20doing.%20So%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20find%20my%20enablers.%20Not%20the%20bad%20kind%20that%20encourages%20me%20to%20go%20bar-hopping%20on%20a%20weeknight%2C%20but%20like-minded%20people%20who%20share%20my%20resolution%2C%20and%20who%20are%20ideally%20already%20working%20out%20regularly.%20For%20me%2C%20having%20a%20gym%20buddy%20will%20help%20keep%20me%20accountable.%20For%20you%2C%20it%20might%20be%20finding%20an%20online%20mindfulness%20community%20or%20an%20evening%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frun-club-making-friends-dating-app-alternatives-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20group%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ET%20is%20for%20time-bound.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Research%20also%20shows%20that%20having%20a%20specific%20time%20frame%2C%20like%206%20months%2C%20makes%20you%20more%20likely%20to%20stick%20to%20your%20goals.%20It%20also%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20measure%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f469b216-d815-47d8-9c72-9f9af2d32d43%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20plan%20to%20give%20myself%20grace%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChanging%20a%20behavior%20is%20one%20thing%2C%20but%20sticking%20to%20it%20is%20the%20hard%20part.%20But%20if%20you%20stick%20with%20it%20long%20enough%2C%20behaviors%20can%20become%20habits.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1002%2Fejsp.674%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%20%3C%2Fa%3Eestimates%20that%20it%20can%20take%20on%20average%2066%20days.%20Of%20course%2C%20this%20can%20vary%20depending%20on%20how%20complex%20the%20behavior%20is%20or%20how%20many%20potential%20barriers%20are%20in%20the%20way.%20But%20consistency%20leads%20to%20automaticity%2C%20a%20fancy%20word%20for%20habit-formation.%20So%20I%20plan%20to%20schedule%20my%20workouts%2C%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20at%20the%20same%20times%2C%20days%2C%20and%20places%20each%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20also%20going%20to%20remind%20myself%20that%20if%20I%20don't%20stick%20to%20my%20resolution%2C%20it's%20not%20%3Cem%3Eall%20%3C%2Fem%3Emy%20fault.%20Don't%20be%20fooled%20by%20some%20of%20the%20life%20coaches%20or%20social%20media%20influencers%20who%20say%20that%20all%20you%20need%20to%20do%20to%20get%20fitter%20or%20healthier%20is%20to%20have%20more%20motivation%20or%20willpower.%20Motivation%20is%20just%20one%20component%20of%20behavior%20change.%20The%20environment%20shapes%20our%20behavior%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsocialactionlab.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fs44159-024-00305-0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccess%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%2C%20to%20necessary%20opportunities%20or%20resources%20we%20do%20or%20don't%20have%2C%20affect%20our%20motivation%20and%20ultimately%20our%20ability%20to%20stick%20to%20goals.%20But%20by%20setting%20a%20SMART%20resolution%2C%20finding%20my%20enablers%2C%20and%20being%20self-compassionate%20and%20consistent%20will%20hopefully%20help%20me%20turn%20my%20resolution%20for%202025%20into%20a%20habit%20by%202026.