0you%20think%20that's%20a%20real%20a%20high%20because%20once%20you%20hit%20the%20ball%20cleanly%20of%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20bat%20and%20it%20goes%20into%20the%20stands%2C%20there%20is%20no%20better%20feeling%20for%20a%20batter.%20Sixer%20is%20a%20different%20feeling%20and%20it's%20a%20drug%2C%20it%20gets%20into%20your%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20difference%20between%20a%20boundary%20and%20a%20six%20is%20just%20two%20runs%20but%20the%20risk%20percentage%20is%20100%20per%20cent.%20Boundary%20is%20hit%20along%20the%20ground%20no%20risk%20at%20all%2C%20a%20six%20is%20attempted%20with%20the%20ball%20up%20in%20the%20air%20and%20if%20you%20don't%20time%20it%2C%20if%20it%20hits%20the%20toe%20of%20your%20bat%2C%20it%20can%20go%20up%20and%20you%20can%20be%20out%20caught.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20particular%20point%20of%20time%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20go%20for%20a%20six%2C%20it%20was%20not%20going%20to%20win%20us%20the%20match.%20There%20was%20a%20long%20on%20there%2C%20there%20was%20a%20deep%20square%20leg%20there%2C%20so%20if%20a%20pull%20shot%20along%20the%20ground%20would%20have%20been%20attempted%20it%20would%20have%20got%20you%20four%20runs%2C%20and%20that%20is%20how%20it%20opened%20the%20door%20for%20Australia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735633260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fb65radq_rishabh-pant-afp_625x300_28_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fsunil-gavaskar-brutally-honest-on-rishabh-pants-dismissal-on-day-5-like-a-drug-7364679%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rishabh%20Pant%20was%20batting%20alongside%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20and%20the%20pair%20added%2088%20runs%20for%20the%203rd%20wicket.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A183%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fsun