the%20AAP%20form%20the%20government%20winning%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20announcmenet%20of%20scheme%2C%20Delhi%20BJP%20President%20Virendraa%20Sachdeva%20on%20Monday%20attacked%20the%20AAP%20government%20after%20and%20said%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20now%20a%20defeated%20and%20desperate%20leader%20who%20is%20making%20%26quot%3Bpopulist%20announcements%20to%20stay%20in%20power.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20the%20Delhi%20BJP%20chief%20said%20that%20the%20AAP%20knows%20they%20are%20going%20to%20lose%20Delhi%20elections%3B%20that's%20why%20they%20are%20remembering%20'Lord%20Ram.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20now%20a%20defeated%20and%20desperate%20leader%20who%20is%20making%20daily%20populist%20announcements%20to%20stay%20in%20power.%20They%20(Delhi%20government)%20have%20to%20reply%20in%20court%2C%20why%20they%20didn't%20pay%20for%20Priests%20and%20Granthis%20like%20Maulavis%20-%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20that%2C%20they%20have%20announced%20this%20scheme%20(Pujari%20Granthi%20Samman%20Yojana)...%20When%20you%20(AAP)%20see%20that%20you%20are%20losing%20ground%2C%20'tumhe%20Ram%20naam%20yaad%20aa%20raha%20hai'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sachdeva%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20pressure%20of%20the%20movement%20by%20the%20Delhi%20BJP%20and%20its%20Pujari%20Prakosht%20for%20more%20than%20two%20years%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20forced%20to%20announce%20the%20Pujari%20Granthi%20Samman%20Yojana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735628220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fcihsra08_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_29_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%