he%20area%2C%20it%20also%20provides%20a%20more%20accessible%20and%20scenic%20route%20between%20these%20two%20monuments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEarlier%2C%20tourists%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20a%20ferry%20service%20to%20travel%20from%20the%20Kanyakumari%20boat%20jetty%20to%20the%20Vivekananda%20Memorial%2C%20and%20then%20on%20to%20the%20Thiruvalluvar%20statue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20glass%20bridge%2C%20visitors%20can%20now%20take%20a%20leisurely%20walk%20between%20the%20two%20monuments%2C%20cutting%20down%20on%20travel%20time%20and%20offering%20a%20more%20comfortable%20alternative.%20The%20breathtaking%20views%20of%20the%20sea%20below%2C%20as%20visitors%20cross%20the%20bridge%2C%20make%20this%20journey%20a%20memorable%20experience%20in%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EDesigned%20like%20a%20bowstring%20arch%2C%20the%20glass%20bridge%20is%20as%20durable%20as%20it%20is%20visually%20striking.%20It%20is%20built%20to%20endure%20the%20region's%20harsh%20marine%20environment%2C%20capable%20of%20resisting%20the%20corrosive%20effects%20of%20salty%20sea%20air%20and%20potential%20damage%20from%20the%20frequent%20exposure%20to%20high%20humidity.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735627320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F761sort_india-glass-bridge_625x300_31_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-s-first-glass-bridge-in-tamil-nadu-connects-2-iconic-monuments-what-you-should-know-7368792%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20glass%20bridge%20in%20Kanyakumari%20offers%20stunning%20views%20of%20the%20sea%20and%20reduces%20travel%20time%20for%20tourists%20between%20Vivekananda%20Rock%20Memorial%20and%20Thiruvalluvar%20statue%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-s-first-glass-bridge-in-tamil-nadu-connects-2-iconic-monuments-what-