us%20months%20before%20that%2C%20it%20never%20fails%20to%20infuse%20us%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20positivity%20and%20hope.%20The%20same%20holds%20true%20for%20this%20year-end%20in%20Indian%20men's%20cricket.%20History%20was%20made%2C%20new%20heroes%20emerged%2C%20and%20legendary%20figures%20called%20it%20a%20day.%20There%20were%20new%20highs%20and%20all-time%20new%20lows.%20But%20the%20sense%20of%20optimism%20lingers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EConquering%20Cape%20Town%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20always%20found%20it%20strange%20that%20South%20Africa%20as%20a%20Test%20venue%20is%20not%20given%20as%20much%20conversation%20time%20as%2C%20say%2C%20Australia%20and%20England.%20It's%20a%20really%20tough%20land%20to%20conquer.%20India%20have%20never%20won%20a%20Test%20series%20there%20and%20in%20nine%20tours%20since%20their%20first%20in%201992%2F93%2C%20have%20lost%20seven%20series%20and%20drawn%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20began%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20dread%20when%20the%20team%20found%20itself%200-1%20down%20in%20a%20two-Test%20series%20in%20the%20Rainbow%20Nation%20after%20losing%20the%20first%20by%20an%20innings%20and%2032%20runs.%20What%20followed%2C%20though%2C%20was%20jaw-dropping%20and%20another%20reminder%20of%20the%20age-old%20adage%20that%20%E2%80%98bowlers%20win%20you%20Test%20matches'.%20We%20saw%20an%20exhibition%20of%20pure%20bowling%20class%20by%20Team%20India%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20in%20Cape%20Town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Proteas%20were%20shot%20out%20for%2055%20in%20their%20first%20innings%20(SA's%20seventh-lowest%20Test%20innings%20total%20of%20all%20time)%2C%20thanks%20largely%20to%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20(6%2F15)%2C%20and%20then%20they%20were%20dismissed%20for%20176%20in%20their%20second%20innings.%20Siraj%20has%20already%20proven%20that%20he%20is%20a%20quality%20Test%20bowler%2C%20but%20what%20was%20really%20encouraging%20to%20see%20was%20the%20supporting%20act.%20Thirty-one-year-old%20Mukesh%20Kumar%20took%20two%20wickets%20in%20SA's%20first%20innings%2C%20giving%20away%20zero%20runs%20in%202.2%20overs.%20He%20finished%20the%20game%20with%20match%20figures%20of%204%2F56.%20Mukesh%2C%20who%20became%20just%20the%20second%20Indian%20cricketer%20after%20T.%20Natarajan%20to%20make%20an%20all-format%20debut%20in%20the%20same%20series%20(vs%20WI%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20in%202023)%2C%20showed%20that%20he%20is%20ready%20for%20Test%20cricket.%20It's%20not%20very%20often%20that%20one%20sees%20India%20chasing%20a%20target%20under%20100%20in%20an%20overseas%20Test%2C%20but%20that's%20the%20impact%20the%20bowlers%20had%2C%20as%20India%20were%20left%20to%20chase%20just%2079%20and%20they%20romped%20home%20to%20a%20seven-wicket%20triumph%2C%20marking%20their%20first%20Test%20win%20in%20Cape%20Town%20and%20drawing%20the%20series.%20All%20this%20left%20us%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20great%20optimism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%20%E2%80%93%20Destined%20for%20Greatness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty-five%20years%20after%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20scored%20700-plus%20runs%20in%20a%20Test%20series%20(for%20a%20second%20time)%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20emulated%20that%20incredible%20feat.%20In%202024%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20added%20glorious%20new%20chapters%20in%20the%20fairytale%20that%20is%20his%20international%20career.%20In%20the%20home%20Test%20series%20vs%20England%2C%20which%20India%20won%204-1%2C%20Jaiswal%20notched%20up%20712%20runs%20and%20became%20the%20third%20youngest%20player%20to%20score%20two%20Test%20double%20tons%20after%20Don%20Bradman%20and%20Vinod%20Kambli.%20He%20was%20the%20highest%20run-getter%20in%20the%20series.%20In%20second%20place%20was%20another%20young%20Indian%20talent%20who%20should%20have%20a%20big%20role%20to%20play%20in%20writing%20the%20future%20of%20Indian%20cricket%3A%20Shubman%20Gill%20(452%20runs).%20Virat%20Kohli%20was%20missing%20from%20the%20series%2C%20but%20it%20was%20refreshing%20to%20see%20young%20guns%20ruling%20the%20batting%20charts.%20The%20next%20generation%20is%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWorld%20Cup%20Win%20After%2016%20Years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20ICC%20tournaments%3A%20since%202013%20and%20before%202024%2C%20this%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20painful%20relationships%20to%20dissect.%20And%20it%20hit%20a%20new%20low%20in%202023%20when%20India%20lost%20an%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20final%20to%20Australia%20at%20home.%20Which%20is%20why%20when%20India%20became%20world%20champions%20in%202024%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202011%2C%20it%20was%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20redemption%20for%20the%20big%20names%20in%20the%20set-up.%20This%20time%2C%20there%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20great%20belief%20in%20the%20Indian%20camp%2C%20and%20with%20each%20win%2C%20the%20fans%20began%20to%20believe%20in%20it%20as%20well.%20The%20team%20didn't%20lose%20that%20belief%20even%20when%20the%20Proteas%20needed%2030%20off%2030%20in%20the%20final%2C%20with%20six%20wickets%20in%20hand.%20The%20fact%20that%20India%20became%20the%20first%20team%20ever%20to%20win%20the%20title%20unbeaten%20went%20a%20long%20way%20in%20showing%20just%20what%20a%20force%20the%20Indian%20men's%20team%20has%20become%20in%20T20Is.%20They%20registered%20their%20highest-ever%20T20I%20total%20(297%2F6)%20vs%20Bangladesh%20in%202024%2C%20which%20is%20also%20the%20highest%20total%20by%20a%20Test-playing%20nation.%20Incredibly%2C%20out%20of%2026%20T20Is%20played%20in%202024%2C%20India%20won%2024.%20That's%20a%20win%20percentage%20of%2092.31%25%2C%20the%20highest%20ever%20by%20any%20team%20in%20a%20calendar%20year.%20Another%20big%20reason%20to%20celebrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20saw%20next%20was%20a%20whole%20slew%20of%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERohit%20%26amp%3B%20Virat%20End%20T20I%20Careers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20T20%20World%20Cup%20win%20gave%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20bring%20the%20curtain%20down%20on%20their%20T20I%20careers.%20It%20was%20a%20good%20call%20too.%20T20%20is%20the%20format%20that%20thrives%20the%20most%20on%20young%20blood%2C%20and%20the%20two%20seniors%2C%20who%20are%20both%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%2030%2C%20knew%20that%20allowing%20the%20next%20generation%20to%20take%20over%20was%20a%20call%20they%20couldn't%20ignore.%20And%20what%20better%20way%20to%20exit%20than%20with%20world%20champions'%20medals%20around%20their%20necks%3F%20The%20championship%20win%20was%20also%20a%20fitting%20farewell%20for%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%3A%20The%20%E2%80%98Surprise'%20Pick%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20needed%20a%20new%20steady%20T20I%20captain.%20The%20buzz%20was%20that%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20who%20was%20being%20tagged%20as%20the%20next%20India%20long-term%20captain%2C%20might%20not%20get%20the%20job%20because%20of%20his%20injury%20concerns.%20And%20that%20was%20a%20fair%20assessment.%20The%20management%20had%20to%20go%20with%20someone%20they%20knew%20would%20be%20available%20at%20all%20times.%20Based%20on%20this%20and%20also%20what%20the%20Chief%20Selector%20called%20%E2%80%9Cgeneral%20feedback%20from%20the%20dressing%20room%E2%80%9D%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20was%20named%20the%20new%20India%20T20I%20captain.%20The%20general%20refrain%20was%20that%20this%20was%20a%20good%20call.%20Surya%20is%20the%20best%20Indian%20batting%20talent%20that%20has%20emerged%20in%20T20s%20in%20recent%20times.%20He%20has%20a%20mature%20head%20on%20his%20shoulders.%20Also%2C%20just%20like%20Hardik%2C%20Surya%20believes%20in%20a%20no-hierarchy%20system.%20It%20was%20good%20to%20hear%20Sanju%20Samson%2C%20who%20recently%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20batter%20to%20score%20two%20consecutive%20T20I%20tons%2C%20say%20that%20what%20gave%20him%20the%20most%20confidence%20was%20Surya's%20backing%20and%20complete%20role%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuru%20Gambhir's%20Rocky%20Start%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWere%20eyebrows%20raised%20when%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20was%20approached%20to%20become%20the%20new%20India%20men's%20team%20Head%20Coach%3F%20Absolutely.%20Gambhir%20had%20been%20a%20mentor%20but%20never%20a%20coach.%20He%20took%20over%20right%20after%20the%20euphoria%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20win%20and%20had%20quite%20a%20rocky%20start%2C%20which%20gave%20his%20critics%20more%20ammunition%20to%20question%20his%20appointment%20as%20India%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELosing%20to%20SL%20After%2027%20Years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESri%20Lanka%20is%20an%20opponent%20India%20are%20expected%20to%20beat%2C%20in%20any%20format%2C%20in%20any%20conditions.%20They%20did%20win%20the%20T20I%20series%2C%20but%20when%20the%20men%20in%20blue%20lost%20to%20the%20other%20men%20in%20blue%20from%20the%20Emerald%20Isles%20in%20an%20away%20ODI%20series%202-0%2C%20marking%20their%20first%20bilateral%20ODI%20series%20loss%20to%20the%20Lankans%20since%201997%2C%20criticism%20for%20the%20players%20and%20coach%20was%20at%20an%20all-year%20high.%20That%20went%20through%20the%20roof%20after%20the%20110-run%20loss%20in%20the%20third%20ODI%2C%20where%20India%20were%20shot%20out%20for%20138%2C%20chasing%20249.%20This%20wasn't%20the%20start%20that%20Gambhir%20wanted%20to%20his%20coaching%20career%2C%20it%20wasn't%20the%20result%20the%20team%20or%20the%20fans%20were%20targeting.%20What%20hurt%20the%20most%20was%20that%20the%20Indian%20batting%20unit%20was%20found%20wanting%20when%20it%20came%20to%20tackling%20spin%20and%20the%20criticism%20was%20fair.%20The%20Lankan%20spinners%20took%2027%20of%20the%2030%20Indian%20wickets%20that%20fell%20in%20the%20series.%20India's%20vulnerability%20in%20particular%20to%20left-arm%20spin%20was%20exposed%20completely%20by%20the%20player%20of%20the%20series%2C%20Dunith%20Wellalage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%200-3%20Drubbing%20That%20Really%20Hurt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spin%20ogre%20has%20been%20haunting%20Indian%20batters%20for%20a%20while%20now%2C%20but%20what%20hurt%20the%20most%20in%202024%20was%20the%20way%20Team%20India%20crumbled%20in%20a%20home%20Test%20series%20to%20an%20opposition%20spin.%20New%20Zealand's%20Test%20series%20win%20was%20a%20gut%20punch.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20India%20were%20whitewashed%200-3%20at%20home.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%2012%20years%2C%20they%20lost%20a%20home%20Test%20series.%20The%20Kiwis%20had%20done%20their%20homework%20and%20had%20studied%20India's%20loss%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20quite%20carefully%3B%20their%20call%20to%20play%20two%20left-arm%20spinners%20(Ajaz%20Patel%20and%20Mitchell%20Santner)%20was%20a%20masterstroke.%20India's%20tactic%20of%20including%20as%20many%20left-hand%20batters%20as%20they%20could%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%20to%20counter%20this%20didn't%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20embarrassing%2C%20to%20be%20fair%2C%20to%20see%20a%20nation%20once%20tagged%20the%20best%20players%20of%20spin%20to%20be%20humbled%20by%20spinners%20in%20their%20own%20backyard.%20Preparing%20rank%20turners%20for%20a%20home%20Test%20series%20cannot%20be%20a%20strategy%20the%20team%20can%20adopt%20going%20forward.%20There's%20no%20doubt%20that%20preparing%20for%20T20%20cricket%20has%20had%20an%20effect%20on%20how%20batters%20approach%20classical%20batting%2C%20but%20what%20about%20rotating%20the%20star%20batters%20such%20that%20they%20are%20given%20periodic%20breaks%20from%20international%20cricket%20to%20play%20domestic%20cricket%3F%20They%20will%20be%20tested%20by%20all%20kinds%20of%20spin%20there%20on%20tracks%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20natural%20turners.%20But%20in%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20the%20practice%20of%20star%20batters%20playing%20domestic%20cricket%20just%20does%20not%20exist%2C%20unless%20they%20are%20dropped%20from%20the%20team%20due%20to%20bad%20form.%20Maybe%20it's%20time%20star%20culture%20made%20way%20for%20a%20more%20pragmatic%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735626600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ft1lvnhn_india-afp_625x300_30_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fworld-cup-win-to-sl-loss-the-rollercoaster-that-indian-cricket-was-in-2024-7368690%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20T20%20World%20Cup%20win%20gave%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20bring%20the%20curtain%20down%20on%20their%20T20I%20careers.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20New%20Zealands%20Test%20series%20win%20was%20a%20gut%20punch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fworld-cup-win-to-sl-loss-the-rollercoaster-that-indian-cricket-was-in-2024-7368690%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22POCO%20X7%20series%20smartphones%20to%20be%20launched%20on%20January%209%3A%20What%20to%20expect%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735626199000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fpoco-x7-series-smartphones-to-be-launched-on-january-9-what-to-expect-124123100282_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20upcoming%20POCO%20X7%205G%20smartphone%20appears%20to%20feature%20a%20Redmi%20Note%2014%20Pro-inspired%20design%20with%20a%20curved%20back%20and%20centrally%20placed%20rear%20camera%20module%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fpoco-x7-series-smartphones-to-be-launched-on-january-9-what-to-expect-124123100282_1.html%22%2C%22cdn