ready-secretly-helping-putin-the-kremlins-take-on-his-bold-plans%2Famp_articleshow%2F116817756.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fis-trump-is-already-secretly-helping-putin-the-kremlins-take-on-his-bold-plans%2Famp_articleshow%2F116817756.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IRCTC%20Website%20Down%20Ahead%20Of%20New%20Year%2C%20Third%20Outage%20This%20Month%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20IRCTC%20or%20Indian%20Railway%20Catering%20and%20Tourism%20Corporation%20website%20and%20mobile%20app%20for%20booking%20train%20tickets%20was%20down%20today%20ahead%20of%20the%20New%20Year%20-%20the%20third%20such%20outage%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20users%20failed%20to%20log%20in%20to%20the%20IRCTC%20website%20and%20those%20who%20could%2C%20were%20unable%20to%20book%20their%20tickets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20major%20outage%20was%20reported%20when%20users%20were%20trying%20to%20book%20Tatkal%20(emergency)%20tickets%20at%2010%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20users%20expressed%20their%20frustration%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%40RailMinIndia%20IRCTC%20website%20is%20down%20from%2010%20am%20today%20%2C%20I%20am%20not%20able%20to%20book%20tatkal%20tickets.%20When%20I%20called%20customer%20care%20they%20are%20saying%20site%20is%20under%20maintenance%2C%20just%20want%20to%20ask%20who%20in%20this%20world%20keep%20the%20site%20under%20maintenance%20in%20working%20hours%3F%20You%20need%20to%20change%20your%20IT%20team%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20user%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIRCTC%20down%20just%20before%20Tatkal%20booking-classic%20timing!%20Anyone%20else%20facing%20the%20same%20issue%3F%20%23IRCTC%20%23TatkalBooking%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20user%20posted%2C%20along%20with%20screenshots%20of%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20I%20try%20to%20book%20a%20train%20ticket%2C%20I%20face%20some%20problems%20in%20the%20IRCTC%20app.%20And%20if%20you%20open%20it%2C%20the%20app%20runs%20so%20slow%20that%20the%20tickets%20get%20exhausted%2C%20the%20railways%20should%20take%20some%20innovative%20steps%20for%20ticket%20booking%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20user%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIRCTC%20server%20down%2C%20No%20tatkal%20booking%20%23IRCTC%20%40IRCTCofficial%20%40RailMinIndia%26quot%3B%2C%20another%20person%20wrote%2C%20sharing%20screenshots%20of%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20third%20time%20in%20this%20month%20that%20IRCTC%20has%20faced%20such%20disruptions.%C2%A0On%20December%2026%2C%20the%20website%20and%20mobile%20app%20were%20down%20for%201.5%20hours%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bmaintenance%20activity%26quot%3B.%20On%20December%209%2C%20the%20website%20was%20down%20for%20an%20hour%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20users%20to%20book%20tickets%20online.%20According%20to%20the%20downtime%20message%2C%20the%20e-ticketing%20service%20was%20unavailable%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bmaintenance%20activity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735625580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fgck73aoo_indian-railways_625x300_06_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Firctc-website-down-ahead-of-new-year-2025-third-outage-this-month-7368561%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20IRCTC%20or%20Indian%20Railway%20Catering%20and%20Tourism%20Corporation%20website%20and%20mobile%20app%20for%20booking%20train%20tickets%20was%20down%20today%20ahead%20of%20the%20New%20Year%20-%20the%20third%20such%20outage%20this%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Firctc-website-down-ahead-of-new-year-2025-third-outage-this-month-7368561%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Option%20Does%20Kerala%20Nurse%20On%20Death%20Row%20In%20Yemen%20Have%3F%20Lawyer%20Tells%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENimisha%20Priya%2C%20the%20Indian%20nurse%20sentenced%20to%20death%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20Yemeni%20national%2C%20still%20has%20legal%20options%20to%20save%20her%20life%20if%20the%20victim's%20family%20pardons%20her%20and%20accepts%20blood%20money%2C%20said%20Subhas%20Chandran%2C%20her%20family's%20lawyer.%20Yemen%20President%20Rashad%20al-Alimi%20on%20Monday%20approved%20Priya's%20death%20sentence%2C%20and%20she%20can%20be%20executed%20in%20a%20month's%20time.%20She%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20killing%20Talal%20Abdo%20Mahdi%2C%20a%20Yemeni%20national%2C%20in%202017.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Chandran%20noted%20that%20in%20Yemen%2C%20Sharia%20law%20prevails%2C%20under%20which%20if%20the%20victim's%20family%20is%20ready%20to%20pardon%20the%20accused%20after%20taking%20diya%20money%20(blood%20money)%2C%20the%20death%20panel%20can%20be%20reversed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20spoke%20to%20some%20legal%20experts%20there%20(Yemen)%20and%20understood%20that%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Judicial%20Council's%20order%2C%20getting%20an%20assent%20from%20the%20President%20is%20the%20formal%20procedure.%20Still%2C%20if%20the%20family%20is%20ready%20to%20accept%20the%20diya%20money%20and%20pardon%20her%2C%20her%20life%20will%20be%20saved%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chandran%2C%20however%2C%20noted%20that%20due%20to%20the%20prevailing%20political%20situation%20in%20Yemen%2C%20negotiations%20with%20the%20Mahdi's%20family%20are%20being%20hindered.%20Yemen%20has%20been%20facing%20a%20civil%20since%202014%20when%20Houthi%20insurgents%20took%20over%20the%20capital%20city%20Sanaa%2C%20which%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20rapid%20Houthi%20takeover%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20facing%20a%20challenge%20in%20this%20due%20to%20the%20prevailing%20political%20situation%20in%20Yemen.%20We%20are%20unable%20to%20travel%20to%20Yemen%2C%20and%20we%20need%20the%20government's%20support%20for%20that.%20If%20the%20Union%20government%20helps%20us%20with%20negations%2C%20the%20Save%20Nimisha%20Priya%20International%20Action%20Council%20is%20ready%20to%20pay%20whatever%20amount%20the%20family%20asks%20as%20diya%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)said%20that%20India%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20sentencing%20of%20Nimisha%20Priya%20in%20Yemen%20and%20extended%20all%20support%20to%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20that%20the%20family%20of%20Priya%20is%20exploring%20relevant%20options.%20The%20government%20is%20extending%20all%20possible%20help%20in%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20MEA%20Spokesperson%2C%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENimisha%20Priya%20Case%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriya%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20killing%20Talal%20Abdo%20Mahdi%2C%20a%20Yemeni%20national%2C%20in%202017.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20she%20was%20sentenced%20to%20death%20by%20a%20trial%20court%20in%20Yemen.%20Since%20then%2C%20her%20family%20has%20been%20fighting%20for%20her%20release.%20They%20approached%20the%20Yemini%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20trial%20court's%20order%2C%20but%20their%20appeal%20was%20rejected%20in%202023.%20Now%2C%20with%20the%20country's%20President%20also%20rejecting%20Priya's%20appeal%2C%20her%20release%20depended%20on%20securing%20forgiveness%20from%20the%20victim's%20family%20and%20their%20tribal%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20native%20of%20Palakkad%2C%20Priya%20is%20a%20trained%20nurse%20who%20worked%20in%20private%20hospitals%20in%20Yemen%20for%20a%20few%20years.%20Her%20husband%20and%20minor%20daughter%20returned%20to%20India%20in%202014%20because%20of%20financial%20reasons.%20The%20same%20year%2C%20Yemen%20was%20gripped%20by%20civil%20war%2C%20and%20they%20could%20not%20go%20back%2C%20as%20the%20country%20stopped%20issuing%20new%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%202015%2C%20Priya%20sought%20Mahdi's%20support%20to%20set%20up%20her%20clinic%20in%20Sana'a%2C%20as%20under%20Yemen's%20law%2C%20only%20nationals%20are%20allowed%20to%20set%20up%20clinics%20and%20business%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20her%20appeal%20plea%20in%20Yemani%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%202015%2C%20Mahdi%20accompanied%20Priya%20to%20Kerala%20when%20she%20came%20for%20a%20month-long%20holiday.%20During%20the%20visit%2C%20he%20stole%20her%20wedding%20photograph%2C%20which%20he%20later%20manipulated%20to%20claim%20that%20he%20was%20married%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20their%20return%2C%20when%20Priya%20started%20the%20clinic%2C%20Mahadi%20started%20cornering%20all%20the%20revenue.%20He%20also%20manipulated%20the%20ownership%20documents%20of%20the%20clinic.%20When%20Nimisha%20Priya%20questioned%20him%20about%20the%20embezzlement%2C%20he%20became%20hostile%20towards%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20began%20to%20take%20money%20out%20of%20her%20monthly%20earnings%20after%20telling%20everyone%20that%20Priya%20was%20his%20wife%20and%20even%20morphed%20their%20pictures%20to%20show%20they%20were%20married.%20In%20her%20plea%2C%20Priya%20alleged%20that%20soon%20the%20harassment%20turned%20into%20physical%20torture%20and%20Mahdi%20also%20seized%20her%20passport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%20plea%2C%20Priya%20even%20approached%20the%20police%20in%20Sanaa%20regarding%20the%20matter%2C%20but%20instead%20of%20taking%20action%20against%20Mahdi%2C%20the%20police%20arrested%20her%20and%20put%20her%20in%20jail%20for%20six%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202017%2C%20Priya%20approached%20the%20warden%20of%20a%20jail%20near%20her%20clinic%2C%20where%20Mahdi%20was%20previously%20jailed%20under%20various%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20warden%20suggested%20that%20she%20should%20try%20to%20sedate%20him%2C%20and%20then%20convince%20him%20to%20give%20her%20passport.%20However%2C%20sedation%20did%20not%20affect%20Mahdi%2C%20who%20was%20a%20substance%20abuser.%20She%