%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116818738.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHailey%20Bieber%20addressed%20rumours%20of%20marriage%20trouble%20with%20Justin%20Bieber%20through%20a%20witty%20Instagram%20post%2C%20dismissing%20the%20speculation.%20Despite%20viral%20TikTok%20videos%20speculating%20about%20their%20relationship%2C%20a%20source%20close%20to%20the%20couple%20stated%20that%20they%20are%20not%20bothered%20by%20the%20constant%20divorce%20rumours.%20Hailey%20and%20Justin%2C%20who%20married%20in%202018%2C%20recently%20renewed%20their%20vows%20in%20Hawaii.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fhailey-bieber-responds-to-divorce-rumors-with-justin-bieber-heres-whats-she-said-%2Farticleshow%2F116818738.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BStakes%20Are%20High%20For%202025%26quot%3B%3A%20Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai's%20Warning%20To%20Employees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGoogle%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20has%20said%20that%202025%20will%20be%20a%20defining%20year%20for%20the%20company%20with%20the%20rapid%20evolution%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI).%20In%20a%20strategy%20meeting%20held%20in%20California%2C%20he%20urged%20staff%20to%20%26quot%3Binternalise%20the%20urgency%20of%20this%20moment%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20%26quot%3Bmove%20faster%20as%20a%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stakes%20are%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pichai%20said%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20reported%20CNBC.%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20disruptive%20moments.%20In%202025%2C%20we%20need%20to%20be%20relentlessly%20focused%20on%20unlocking%20the%20benefits%20of%20this%20technology%20and%20solving%20real%20user%20problems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Google's%20primary%20focuses%20for%20the%20upcoming%20year%20is%20its%20ambitious%20push%20into%20AI%20through%20the%20Gemini%20app.%20The%20app%2C%20which%20provides%20users%20with%20a%20range%20of%20tools%2C%20is%20seen%20as%20central%20to%20Google's%20strategy%20to%20maintain%20its%20edge%20in%20a%20growing%20field%20of%20generative%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pichai%20acknowledged%20the%20growing%20momentum%20around%20Gemini%2C%20particularly%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20but%20he%20also%20said%20that%20there%20was%20a%20need%20for%20continued%20effort%20to%20position%20the%20app%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20Gemini%20app%2C%20there%20is%20strong%20momentum%2C%20particularly%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months.%20But%20we%20have%20some%20work%20to%20do%20in%202025%20to%20close%20the%20gap%20and%20establish%20a%20leadership%20position%20there%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScaling%20Gemini%20to%20reach%20a%20broader%20consumer%20base%20will%20be%20one%20of%20Google's%20top%20priorities%20for%202025.%20Mr%20Pichai%20outlined%20ambitious%20goals%20for%20the%20app%2C%20targeting%20500%20million%20users%20in%20the%20same%20league%20as%20other%20flagship%20Google%20products.%20%26quot%3BScaling%20Gemini%20on%20the%20consumer%20side%20will%20be%20our%20biggest%20focus%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20December%2018%20meeting%20took%20place%20as%20Google%20is%20under%20intense%20scrutiny%2C%20especially%20after%20a%20series%20of%20legal%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20ruled%20that%20the%20US-based%20tech%20giant%20illegally%20maintains%20a%20monopoly%20in%20the%20search%20market%2C%20while%20other%20ongoing%20investigations%20threaten%20to%20reshape%20the%20company's%20operations.%20Despite%20these%20hurdles%2C%20Mr%20Pichai%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20company%20must%20remain%20focused%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20lost%20on%20me%20that%20we%20are%20facing%20scrutiny%20across%20the%20world.%20It%20comes%20with%20our%20size%20and%20success.%20It's%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20trend%20where%20tech%20is%20now%20impacting%20society%20at%20scale.%20So%20more%20than%20ever%2C%20through%20this%20moment%2C%20we%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20don't%20get%20distracted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScaling%20Gemini%20to%20a%20consumer%20base%20of%20500%20million%20users%20is%20one%20of%20Google's%20most%20ambitious%20goals%2C%20Mr%20Pichai%20said.%20Despite%20facing%20increasing%20competition%2C%20he%20noted%20that%20being%20%26quot%3Bfirst%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20always%20necessary%20for%20success.%20%26quot%3BIn%20history%2C%20you%20don't%20always%20need%20to%20be%20first%20but%20you%20have%20to%20execute%20well%20and%20really%20be%20the%20best%20in%20class%20as%20a%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20what%202025%20is%20all%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20also%20saw%20demonstrations%20of%20upcoming%20AI%20tools%2C%20including%20the%20Jules%20coding%20assistant%20and%20an%20AI-powered%20notetaking%20product%2C%20NotebookLM.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735623360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F351d3hag_sundar-pichai_625x300_11_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsundar-pichai-warns-google-employees-the-stakes-are-high-for-2025-7368342%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20has%20said%20that%202025%20will%20be%20a%20defining%20year%20for%20the%20company%20with%20the%20rapid%20evolution%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsundar-pichai-warns-google-employees-the-stakes-are-high-for-2025-7368342%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20rubs%20more%20salt%