ent%20sector%20for%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20focusing%20on%20human%20rights.%20We%20were%20inspired%20to%20take%20up%20initiatives%20that%20boost%20the%20income%20of%20rural%20residents.%E2%80%9D%20Besides%20her%20role%20in%20the%20association%2C%20Anusuya%20also%20works%20as%20a%20translator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20innovative%20approach%20not%20only%20addresses%20the%20waste%20problem%20but%20also%20generates%20additional%20income%20for%20farmers.%20Currently%2C%20at%20least%201%2C000%20farmers%20across%20Kordha%2C%20Cuttack%2C%20and%20Puri%20districts%20of%20Odisha%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20approach%20provides%20a%20valuable%20template%20for%20rural%20development%20and%20demonstrates%20the%20potential%20of%20waste-to-wealth%20initiatives%20in%20promoting%20sustainable%20agricultural%20practices%20and%20improving%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20rural%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kasinath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20every%20stem%2C%20we%20give%20Rs%2070-80%20to%20a%20farmer.%20By%20collecting%20waste%20from%20farm%20sites%2C%20we%20clean%20their%20field.%20This%20indirectly%20helps%20them%20as%20it%20saves%20them%20labour%20costs.%20On%20average%2C%20a%20farmer%20associated%20with%20us%20earns%20an%20additional%20Rs%207%2C000%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20banana%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%E2%80%99s%20impact%20extends%20beyond%20the%20economic%20realm.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20removing%20banana%20waste%20from%20the%20fields%2C%20this%20approach%20contributes%20to%20a%20cleaner%20environment.%20The%20elimination%20of%20open%20burning%20prevents%20air%20pollution%20and%20mitigates%20the%20risk%20of%20soil%20contamination%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kasinath%2C%20this%20work%20is%20purely%20selfless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20association%20of%20farmers.%20Around%2040%20people%20are%20employed%20here%20to%20handle