r%20acre%2C%20which%20he%20sells%20at%20Rs%20250%20per%20kilogram.%20This%20generates%20annual%20profits%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20loyal%20market%20for%20exotic%20fruits%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnshul%20has%20built%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base%20for%20this%20exotic%20fruit%20in%20his%20hometown%20of%20Shahjahanpur%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20nearby%20districts%20of%20Bareilly%2C%20Farrukhabad%2C%20and%20Hardoi.%20%E2%80%9COur%20dragon%20fruits%20are%20in%20high%20demand%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20exotic%20fruit%2C%20rural%20residents%20often%20use%20it%20as%20a%20gift.%20Panchayat%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20%3Cem%3Epradhan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20buy%20it%20to%20gift%20to%20the%20Block%20Development%20Officer%20(BDO).%20The%20Sub-Divisional%20Officer%20(SDM)%20purchases%20it%20to%20present%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%2C%20and%20newlyweds%20buy%20it%20for%20their%20in-laws%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anshul%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20got%20the%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Governor%20Anandiben%20Patel%20during%20an%20event.%20%E2%80%9CI%20gifted%20dragon%20fruits%20from%20my%20farm%20to%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20appreciated%20my%20work%2C%20and%20it%20was%20really%20encouraging.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDD9uC_PS50G%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDD9uC_PS50G%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3