%2C%20the%20Indian%20Government%20introduced%20the%20Ayushman%20Vaya%20Vandana%20Card%20on%20September%2012%2C%202024%2C%20a%20welcoming%20initiative%20aimed%20at%20ensuring%20that%20financial%20constraints%20no%20longer%20stand%20in%20the%20way%20of%20healthcare%20for%20senior%20citizens%20aged%2070%20and%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20scheme%20provides%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329837%2Fmadurai-doctor-maruti-eco-ambulance-that-treats-elderly-people-with-disability-at-home-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efree%20medical%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20coverage%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20per%20year%20to%20all%20eligible%20senior%20citizens%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20financial%20background.%20Designed%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(AB%20PM-JAY)%2C%20the%20card%20is%20a%20lifeline%20for%20elderly%20individuals%2C%20offering%20them%20access%20to%20quality%20healthcare%20without%20worrying%20about%20the%20cost.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-gallery%20wp-block-gallery-1%20wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20800px)%20100vw%2C%20800px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fwarga-emas_11zon-1734669896.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senior%20citizens%20deserve%20to%20enjoy%20their%20final%20innings%20without%20financial%20worries%20and%20medical%20hassles.%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22391137%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2