in%20Marathi%20using%20the%20Swalekhan%20app.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20partnered%20with%20some%20blind%20schools%20in%20Pune%20and%20taught%20Class%204%20to%20Class%208%20children%20how%20to%20understand%20audio%20instructions%20and%20type%20without%20a%20scribe%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uma%20shares.%20In%20just%20eight%20months%2C%20they%20taught%201%2C200%20children%20across%20Maharashtra%20how%20to%20type%20in%20Marathi.%20The%20app%20is%20now%20being%20used%20by%20over%202%2C000%20children%2C%20with%20around%20150%20taking%20their%20exams%20independently%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20government%20support%2C%20the%20app%20has%20expanded%20its%20reach%2C%20including%20a%20Hindi%20version%20and%20plans%20to%20integrate%20it%20into%20the%20National%20Centre%20for%20Intelligence.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20West%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20a%20scribe.%20They%20teach%20touch%20typing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Uma%20adds.%20Through%20Swalekhan%2C%20Niwant%20is%20now%20helping%20reshape%20the%20future%20of%20visually%20impaired%20students%20in%20India%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20take%20charge%20of%20their%20education%20without%20relying%20on%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENiwant%E2%80%99s%20growth%20story%20is%20intertwined%20with%20the%20Badve%20family%E2%80%99s%20dedication.%20Uma%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20dad%20turned%2060%2C%20he%20left%20his%20business%20and%20joined%20my%20mother.%20The%20number%20of%20students%20we%20had%20coming%20in%20grew%2C%20so%20it%20was%20good%20that%20along%20with%20the%20volunteers%20and%20teachers%2C%20she%20had%20more%20help.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeera%20and%20her%20husband%20started%20by%20providing%20basic%20education%20and%20braille%20resources%20and%20then%20expanded%20to%20include%20classes%20for%20competitive%20exams%2C%20like%20banking%20and%20government%20jobs.%20Over%20200%20Niwant%20students%20are%20now%20employed%20in%20government%20jobs%2C%20particula